```python
client.create_user(username="", password="")

    "password1": str,

```python
client.create_user(username="", password="")
```

{

pull_request.title: Describe how to use token-based matching
pull_request.body: In the example of [README.md](https://github.com/doccano/spacy-partial-tagger/blob/main/README.md), entities are extracted by character-based matching. However, in some cases, character-based matching may not be suitable (e.g., the element symbol `na` for sodium matches the name). This PR add the description of how to use token-based matching to create the training dataset.
